@lassekongo83 Hi. `##div.ad-banner` is a common bait. Triggers antiadblock on many sites. Similar rule (`##.ad-banner`) was removed from EasyList and our filter.

@hoang-rio Hi. `@@||go.kecapku.com/js/ads.js$domain=go.kecapku.com` can be used here. 
By default, EasyList and AdGuard filters don't block this request due anti-adblock problems.
